                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/1951.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister to
                            Switzerland</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                        State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berne</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-10-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 8, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Republic of China was recognized by the Swiss Government on October 8.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stovall</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
